{"tid":571217,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"九巴如因工業行動解僱車長　工會不排除罷工","createTime":"2018-02-24T12:37:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-24T13:07:22.000Z","uid":156363,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"96e880154889b7f3325df890006085b8fed2d54d","tid":571217,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T12:37:20.000Z","msg":"九巴車長組織「月薪車長大聯盟」定於晚上8時發起工業行動。<br />\n<br />\n九巴發出內部通告，指如有任何違反工作指引的行為，公司必定作出嚴厲紀律處分。<br />\n<br />\n九巴僱員工會主席郭志誠回應說，如果公司因為工業行動而解僱車長，工會不排除發起罷工。<br />\n<br />\n郭志誠質疑九巴有大筆收入，但不向員工加薪，又指九巴以紀律處分及解僱等恐嚇員工，他批評是荒謬。<br />\n<br />\n郭志誠說勞工處沒介入今次事件，他要求勞工處、運輸署及行政長官林鄭月娥跟進。"},{"pid":"c3f30654bc8bc2c4fd227f53c99ad166b643f5a9","tid":571217,"uid":156363,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T12:38:49.000Z","msg":"成個工會得3個人，真係唔知講咩好。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ea3fa43aa397069a62ba6ab84eb47344f863260","tid":571217,"uid":124585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T13:05:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/24/210545_7938c28bf0feb61d43ba781998d09c70.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F24%2F210545_7938c28bf0feb61d43ba781998d09c70.gif&h=7e65737c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8d99c02d517c84ca389c30502e8e84f2a44a79ad","tid":571217,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T13:07:22.000Z","msg":"得啖笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}